From: Ian Rogers <irogers@google.com>
Date: Tue, 27 May 2025 20:26:36 -0700
Subject: perf test trace_summary: Skip --bpf-summary tests if no libbpf
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 6dd7a0fde91f252858f4d4cff4245577319b7b88
Patch-mainline: v6.16-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update

If perf is built without libbpf (e.g. NO_LIBBPF=1) then the
--bpf-summary perf trace tests will fail.

Skip the tests as this is expected behavior.

